        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Probus clubs</strong> ‚Äî Social clubs specifically for retirees</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Men's Sheds</strong> ‚Äî Workshop-based social groups for men</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-blue-500 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Community centres</strong> ‚Äî Various programs at Wickham, Hamilton, etc.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

