      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We may be biased, but table tennis genuinely offers unique benefits for older adults:
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-2 my-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Low impact</strong> ‚Äî No running, jumping, or jarring movements</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Play at your pace</strong> ‚Äî Can be gentle rallies or intense competition</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Cognitive benefits</strong> ‚Äî Quick decision-making keeps your brain active</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Balance and coordination</strong> ‚Äî Helps maintain these crucial skills</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Intergenerational</strong> ‚Äî Play with people of all ages</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
