        Worried you're too old, too unfit, or too inexperienced? Here's the reality:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 my-4">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>We have members in their 80s</strong> ‚Äî Age is not a barrier</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>No experience needed</strong> ‚Äî Many start as complete beginners</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Equipment provided</strong> ‚Äî Just bring yourself and comfortable shoes</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <span class="text-green-500 mr-2">‚úì</span>
          <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Welcoming atmosphere</strong> ‚Äî Our members love helping newcomers</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

