          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Is table tennis too fast for older adults?</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Not at all. You can play at whatever pace suits you. Social play is about keeping the ball going, not smashing winners. Many of our most regular players are over 60.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
