          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">Our sessions are mixed-age, which many members prefer. Saturday afternoons tend to have more retired members as working people are often busy. The atmosphere is always welcoming regardless of age.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
